{"tid":1584360,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人到了獨立建國的時候","createTime":"2019-09-21T05:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T23:41:51.000Z","uid":258731,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8cd33521eb476a2fc4fb4453d653a1424cc12c95","tid":1584360,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:27:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">五大訴求的陷阱 滅共自治才是出路</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家其實有冇諗過如果中共回應五大訴求？你唔擔保佢唔會比流嘢你？<br />\n<br />\n撤回條例已經係最好例子，話動議撤回就呃鳩你哋啲市民係撤回，最慘係一部分港豬真係信，已無再出嚟遊行，無再出嚟抗爭。<br />\n但係黑警暴力，無差別襲擊，文革式清算有冇停過？係無呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n獨立調查委員會，佢可以擺自己友入去。佢玩晒<br />\n<br />\n撤回暴動定性，佢撤回完再告你第二條罪<br />\n<br />\n釋放義士，你仲要驚呀，放咗出嚟之後，中共夠擔死將啲抗爭者被自殺，跳樓可以無巨響，出血量可以unreasonably地少，太子831可以被消失。<br />\n<br />\n雙真普選，佢推個班自己友入局又得，操控選舉又得，蛇齋餅糭掌心雷又得，得咗。到時中共面對外國政府challenge，中共仲可以更加大聲理直氣壯咁話香港個政府係普選出嚟嘅。<br />\n<br />\n因為而家我哋已經無嘢可以好輸，如果我哋就咁俾場運動完結，最後受害，被批鬥，被清算係每一個真。香港人。前線於是，和理非也如是。警察已經將文革係各中小學重演，唔駛好耐就會到其他界別。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ABStqQr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FABStqQr.jpg&h=c310024c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老師心聲：警察已經將文革帶入校園<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563034\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563034</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有幾多人認同<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13b0be99df6761420b1a031a8168e0e94d3fd01","tid":1584360,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:28:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"3a33c756837d2ca70ee24b05ba82e3f5658606a7","tid":1584360,"uid":282777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:31:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c9d74e2237bd7c79e6f8612f4977a3fbd83ab08","tid":1584360,"uid":34927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:49:22.000Z","msg":"除左將個價叫高d之外，獨立先係真正可以解決香港始終會比大陸干擾既局面"},{"pid":"040b930791ce5fe994230e0c33287daf4538cde9","tid":1584360,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c9d74e2237bd7c79e6f8612f4977a3fbd83ab08","tid":1584360,"uid":34927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:49:22.000Z","msg":"除左將個價叫高d之外，獨立先係真正可以解決香港始終會比大陸干擾既局面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:50:06.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"9f9d6aaf211fd1fd37dcdc0f48c21e6734e920a3","tid":1584360,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:51:05.000Z","msg":"one step at a time"},{"pid":"fbf66b77fface1855a0e7c7b76a92cb2b9d93f05","tid":1584360,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T06:02:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ca4f09faddc645281a204617c220f0cd438f19b","tid":1584360,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:55:26.000Z"